http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Thiruvananthapuram/Property-tax-payment-online/article14020777.ece

Facility to remit property tax online will soon be introduced in 100 villages, Revenue Minister Adoor Prakash has said.Inaugurating the mini civil station at Varkala in the district on Monday, the Minister said 1.82 crore e-certificates had been issued by the Revenue Department that was being modernised to make it citizen-friendly.Transfer of Registry is being issued with in 24 hours.The Minister said title deeds would be issued to 3,000 residents of the coastal areas in the capital district. The two floors of the proposed five-storey mini civil station were constructed at a cost of Rs.4.14 crore.